HEADWORD: Expiate
<hw>Ex"pi*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>expiatus</ets>,p. p]</ety> <def>Terminated.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expiation</ent>⟦br⟧
